sequenceDiagram
  participant PS as PYNQ MMIO
  participant AXI as AXI-Lite Regs
  participant IP as JY901 I2C IP
  participant JY as JY901

  PS->>AXI: configure DEV_ADDR=0x50, START_REG=0x34, WORD_COUNT=13
  PS->>AXI: write CTRL.enable + oneshot_start
  AXI->>IP: start burst read
  IP->>JY: START + 0xA0
  JY-->>IP: ACK
  IP->>JY: register 0x34
  JY-->>IP: ACK
  IP->>JY: RESTART + 0xA1
  JY-->>IP: ACK
  JY-->>IP: 26 data bytes
  IP->>JY: NACK + STOP
  IP->>AXI: latch 13 raw words, data_valid=1, sample_cnt++
  PS->>AXI: read STATUS and AX_RAW..TEMP_RAW

